data.description: This charming 4 bedroom, 1 bathroom home includes many updates. New roof (2022), bathroom vanity, and paint. New countertops, flooring, tile and dishwasher were recently added to the bright kitchen. This home has a new sewer line and chimney work recently completed in 2020. Centrally located and close to Riverfront Park, shopping, restaurants, I-90, GU district and several more parks.
